items.badge_description: Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 55 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 12!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 200 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 41!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 15 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 4!
